表格群组权限的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('GroupProgramMap')
and type = 'U')
drop table GroupProgramMap
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: GroupProgramMap */
/*==============================================================*/
create table GroupProgramMap (
ID int identity(1,1),
GroupID varchar(50) not null,
ProgramID varchar(50) not null,
AddFlag char(1) null,
CnlFlag char(1) null,
MdyFlag char(1) null,
QuyFlag char(1) null,
PrtFlag char(1) null,
ChkFlag char(1) null,
ChkFlagNO char(1) null,
Remark nvarchar(200) null,
aDate datetime not null constraint DF_GroupProgramMap_aDate default getdate(),
mDate datetime not null constraint DF_GroupProgramMap_mDate default getdate(),
constraint PK_GroupProgramMap primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
